{"tid":493798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： 港鐵搵「龍哥」解鬧鬼疑雲︰真係好多軌 - 李八方","createTime":"2017-12-09T02:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T04:24:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc83f071c86cbd1f88d50e564d215c79d9a267c4","tid":493798,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171209/20239422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F20239422&d=aAykAqn9Fjiz0GAmjPOR9EjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=e0d26052\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F20239422&h=6b58440e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171209/20239422</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n港鐵搵「龍哥」解鬧鬼疑雲︰真係好多軌 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直以嚟港鐵都流傳好多鬼古，噚日又有網民喺網上聲稱朋友影到港鐵車廠有女鬼，仲繪影繪聲話早幾晚柴灣港鐵車廠，有人「見一女鬼披頭散髮，長髮到腰着白袍企喺路口唔郁，嚇到全部伙記縮晒入房唔敢出嚟」。張相放大後見到一白衣女子朦朧身影，唔少網民睇完都話好恐怖，但有眼利網民就質疑話，相中「女鬼」似孭住手袋。唔知係咪鬧鬼傳聞搞到港鐵員工人心惶惶，港鐵傍晚就喺官方facebook專頁上載短片，話訪問咗一位車廠員工「龍哥」，呢位「龍哥」話聽到車廠有同事見鬼，於是去「探靈」。最後佢話得啖笑：「車廠真係好多『鬼』，路『軌』吖嗎！」佢話相中女鬼只係港鐵一個女同事，係「人」。但係個女同事點解半夜三更落車廠，佢就冇再解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171209/large/a1306a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171209%2Flarge%2Fa1306a.gif&h=5c8805ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衣女子深夜出現喺柴灣車廠，惹來鬧鬼傳聞。互聯網"},{"pid":"e521238f929b7c2fb25995d33ecc4735e9699a82","tid":493798,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"其實佢望住嗰邊既先係有......."},{"pid":"8e93f6197592aac121eb587d918e2f37317ebb15","tid":493798,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"車九！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850956bfc40c53b291b7de53cef3c31ee4fac619","tid":493798,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"家下做乜撚野遮<br />\n佢有解釋到咩<br />\n痴孖根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814cca1ce6462e10c2a22e09acef21332e0b276d","tid":493798,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:10:21.000Z","msg":"一個話係女同事 一個話係鬼<br />\n同d 八婆阿伯係公園鳩up 有乜分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要玩祥仔既食字gag <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2070b7e5f8e0a96064577106a5b5d96bbae88a","tid":493798,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家下做乜撚野遮<br />\n佢有解釋到咩<br />\n痴孖根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉，佢點知係女同事？"},{"pid":"73932c4251640a28979bef50d84392a97c2e7367","tid":493798,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢望住嗰邊既先係有.......</blockquote><br />\n又係你條撚樣"},{"pid":"d79be4984fa5d9bfa54fd1bb015bd5fa34efb303","tid":493798,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"基哥呢?"},{"pid":"32b8f842266dd4c514c28f895983bbe9f893422a","tid":493798,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"係，軌係多嘅"}]}